{"tid":18029,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偽造醫生紙騙有薪假　護理員判服務令","createTime":"2016-12-02T05:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T05:22:45.000Z","uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3357d47de49d3162c735925c2ff5706830f5878","tid":18029,"uid":22680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/OFKNcqlRZSidiGr0szE5DQ--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztmaT1pbnNldDtoPTQwMDtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc5O3c9NTAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20161202a122404.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOFKNcqlRZSidiGr0szE5DQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztmaT1pbnNldDtoPTQwMDtpbD1wbGFuZTtxPTc5O3c9NTAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20161202a122404.jpg&h=e84d2378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】瑪嘉烈醫院前護理員於前年10月至去年2月期間，偽造5份醫生證明書，從而獲得7日有薪病假，而不從薪酬中扣除2726元，導致醫管局蒙受不利，護理員早前承認一項欺詐罪，今判100小時社會服務令。<br />\n　　被告甘慧聰（36歲）求情指自己犯案愚蠢，並呈上聖約翰救傷隊和醫院同事撰寫的求情信；裁判官判刑指被告認罪，報告正面， 為了2000多元，令過往工作努力白費，行為十分不智，最終判社會服務令。<br />\n　　法庭記者：潘琪慧<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%81%BD%E9%80%A0%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%99%E9%A8%99%E6%9C%89%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87-%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E5%93%A1%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E4%BB%A4-042200811.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2581%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B4%2599%25E9%25A8%2599%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%2596%25AA%25E5%2581%2587-%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E4%25BB%25A4-042200811.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK94scwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=376ff2c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%81%BD%E9%80%A0%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%99%E9%A8%99%E6%9C%89%E8%96%AA%E5%81%87-%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E5%93%A1%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E4%BB%A4-042200811.html</a>"}]}